comment: Beal (WAS) maintains legal guarding position on Conley's (MEM) move toward the basket.
Gortat (WAS) is in the restricted area at the time of the contact with Green (MEM).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of a blocking foul is confirmed.
Ennis III (MEM) obtains a legal guarding position and is outside of the restricted area at the time of the contact with Wall (WAS).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of an offensive foul is confirmed.
Carter (MEM) and Gortat (WAS) briefly engage and separate off ball.
Gasol (MEM) makes incidental contact with Porter (WAS) during rebounding.
Conley (MEM) commits a take foul on Wall (WAS).
Oubre Jr. (WAS) makes contact with Conley's (MEM) body that affects his jump shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor that Conley (MEM) was attempting a 3pt field goal when fouled is confirmed.
Green (MEM) commits a take foul on Beal (WAS).
Gasol (MEM) makes incidental contact with Beal (WAS) that does not affect his SQBR.
